import React from 'react'
import * as ReactDOMClient from 'react-dom/client'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import { BrowserRouter } from 'react-router-dom'
const rootElement = document.getElementById('root')
const root = ReactDOMClient.createRoot
(rootElement)
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <BrowserRouter>
    <App />
    </BrowserRouter>
  </React.StrictMode>
)
